{"tid":1587280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"香港01\"呢份紅底報紙一定要小心，專門出賣抗爭者，所以佢地推出黎將會參選果d所謂抗爭勇士都要小心！","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:03:55.000Z","uid":241151,"like":38,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b07b73270cb3a1b775f9bd718153ad4a7f5282a5","tid":1587280,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LAnYdiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAnYdiQ.jpg&h=2d39a630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警，藍絲，大公民匯，撐共產黨既人易防，擺明係敵人！<br />\n<br />\n表面扮到好支持&quot;民主&quot;，又扮到好&quot;青年&quot;抗爭，又扮到好&quot;本土&quot;又話企係&quot;前線&quot;既不同黨派，同埋扮到好撐民主同抗爭，甚至激進既不同&quot;生果&quot;不同&quot;立場&quot;既所謂尖&quot;端&quot;傳媒及網媒，係必要時總係會忽左忽右，背棄香港市民，變相維穩，所以一定要小心<br />\n到今時今日，網上仲有人推舉叫人係前線捉鬼，想孤立前線抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎泛民左膠繼續話我係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地除咗叫人起我底同埋不推文回覆之外仲有邊句？好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffba6c2b2d4cc8f2a5ab18fcfe49f1b2e52fa274","tid":1587280,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f69143e8894de6ecc3539a894236c84148c7239","tid":1587280,"uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此為本post最後一個回覆<br />\n不推文回覆都慳番<br />\n樓主呢條on9應該好多人認得<br />\n樓下回post 死全家</span>"},{"pid":"e698b381db809f838bcfd1cc0bed6c877cb997e2","tid":1587280,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f69143e8894de6ecc3539a894236c84148c7239","tid":1587280,"uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:42:34.00